title: Sample Book, "Alfred Peats Wallpaper, No. 5", 1915
creditline: Gift of Disa and Doug Clarner
description: Selection of wallpaper samples, bound in embossed black paper cover. Samples include Tekko, ingrain, oatmeal, embossed border, crepe, imitation grasscloth and leather, sanitary papers with borders, and ceiling papers.  Each design is shown in multiple colorways.
